com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.GetAzureTargetBucketNamesRequestHandler.documentation=\
Gets all Microsoft Azure custom bucket name mappings between local BP buckets and their Microsoft Azure target blob containers.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.GetAzureTargetFailuresRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.GetAzureTargetFailuresRequestHandler.documentation=\
Gets all failures.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.GetAzureTargetReadPreferenceRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.GetAzureTargetReadPreferenceRequestHandler.documentation=\
