com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.GetAzureTargetReadPreferencesRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.GetAzureTargetReadPreferencesRequestHandler.documentation=\
Gets all read preferences that override the default read preference of the target.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.GetAzureTargetRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.GetAzureTargetRequestHandler.documentation=\
Gets the specified target.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.GetAzureTargetsRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.GetAzureTargetsRequestHandler.documentation=\
