com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.ImportAzureTargetRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.ImportAzureTargetRequestHandler.documentation=\
Imports the designated cloud bucket on the designated target into this appliance.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.ModifyAllAzureTargetsRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.ModifyAllAzureTargetsRequestHandler.documentation=\
Modifies all Azure targets.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.ModifyAzureTargetRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.ModifyAzureTargetRequestHandler.documentation=\
Modifies the specified Azure target.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.RegisterAzureTargetRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.azure.RegisterAzureTargetRequestHandler.documentation=\
