com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.ds3.CreateDs3TargetReadPreferenceRequestHandler.documentation=\
Create a DS3 replication target read preference for a particular bucket, overriding the default defined in the DS3 replication target itself.

