com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.ds3.DeleteDs3TargetFailureRequestHandler.documentation=\
Delete the specified DS3 target failure.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.ds3.DeleteDs3TargetReadPreferenceRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.ds3.DeleteDs3TargetReadPreferenceRequestHandler.documentation=\
Delete the specified replication target read preference.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.ds3.DeleteDs3TargetRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.ds3.DeleteDs3TargetRequestHandler.documentation=\
Delete the specified DS3 replication target.

