com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.ds3.RegisterDs3TargetRequestHandler.documentation=\
Attempt to connect to the specified DS3 target and register it.  If it cannot be connected to, this \
request will fail.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.ds3.PairBackRegisteredDs3TargetRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.ds3.PairBackRegisteredDs3TargetRequestHandler.documentation=\
Pairs back an already registered DS3 target to the source.

