com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.ds3.VerifyDs3TargetRequestHandler.documentation=\
Verifies connectivity to the target and that the admin credentials are good.  \
If full_details is specified, verifies that all data expected to reside on the target does in fact reside there.

