com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.CreateS3TargetReadPreferenceRequestHandler.documentation=\
Creates a AWS S3 read preference that overrides the default read preference of the target.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.DeleteS3TargetBucketNameRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.DeleteS3TargetBucketNameRequestHandler.documentation=\
Deletes a AWS S3 custom bucket name mapping between a local BP bucket and a AWS S3 target blob container.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.DeleteS3TargetFailureRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.DeleteS3TargetFailureRequestHandler.documentation=\
Deletes the specified failure.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.DeleteS3TargetReadPreferenceRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.DeleteS3TargetReadPreferenceRequestHandler.documentation=\
Deletes a AWS S3 read preference that overrides the default read preference of the target.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.DeleteS3TargetRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.DeleteS3TargetRequestHandler.documentation=\
Deletes the specified AWS S3 target.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetBlobsOnS3TargetRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetBlobsOnS3TargetRequestHandler.documentation=\
Gets all the blobs that reside on a given S3 target.

