com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetS3TargetBucketNamesRequestHandler.documentation=\
Gets all AWS S3 custom bucket name mappings between local BP buckets and their AWS S3 target blob containers.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetS3TargetFailuresRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetS3TargetFailuresRequestHandler.documentation=\
Gets all failures.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetS3TargetReadPreferenceRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetS3TargetReadPreferenceRequestHandler.documentation=\
Gets the specified read preferences that overrides the default read preference of the target.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetS3TargetReadPreferencesRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetS3TargetReadPreferencesRequestHandler.documentation=\
Gets all read preferences that override the default read preference of the target.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetS3TargetRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetS3TargetRequestHandler.documentation=\
Gets the specified target.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetS3TargetsRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.GetS3TargetsRequestHandler.documentation=\
Gets all S3 targets.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.ImportS3TargetRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.target.s3.ImportS3TargetRequestHandler.documentation=\
Imports the designated cloud bucket on the designated target into this appliance.

