com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.user.DelegateCreateUserRequestHandler.documentation=\
Users must be created via the management path.  \
This request handler will delegate a create user request to the management path.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.user.DelegateDeleteUserRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.user.DelegateDeleteUserRequestHandler.documentation=\
Users must be deleted via the management path.  \
This request handler will delegate a delete user request to the management path.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.user.GetUserRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.user.GetUserRequestHandler.documentation=\
Get the specified user.

com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.user.GetUsersRequestHandler.version=1
com.spectralogic.s3.server.handler.reqhandler.spectrads3.user.GetUsersRequestHandler.documentation=\
Get all users.

